  "text": "On the basis of comprehensive ultrasound imaging, we presumed the disease stage (The International Federation of Gynecologists and Obstetricians [FIGO] 2014), required surgical procedures, and the surgical complexity if primary debulking surgery was attempted. The calculation of surgical complexity was based on a scoring system described elsewhere [CITATION_1] and facilitated with a web-based calculator (available online: http://gin-onc-calculators.com/lp.php). In accordance with imaging and patients' clinical data, we suggested management strategies: upfront surgery or diagnostic laparoscopy followed by neoadjuvant chemotherapy.",
